{"tid":2422603,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"向家移民台灣失敗！","createTime":"2021-02-25T09:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T10:25:53.000Z","uid":258815,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6186d94bb5f90449973c19e5b2e4c80098996f72","tid":2422603,"uid":258815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:55:53.000Z","msg":"香港影視大亨「龍五」向華強及長子向佐，去年底向移民署申請依親移民，移民署今證實，經過相關單位審查，認有「香港澳門居民進入臺灣地區及居留定居許可辦法」第22條所規定不予許可情形，內政部依規定不予許可居留。對於被駁回一事，「向太」陳嵐回應《蘋果新聞網》說：「事情總有水落石出的一天。」她表示不願多說，但有可能的話會再申請。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，相關單位是以規定中的<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">「有危害國家利益、公共安全、公共秩序或從事恐怖活動之虞」駁回向氏父子的申請。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210225/K7JUREQGWRBCFOYV4HI6TG574U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210225%2FK7JUREQGWRBCFOYV4HI6TG574U%2F&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=f901cd54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210225%2FK7JUREQGWRBCFOYV4HI6TG574U%2F&h=7647c5b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210225/K7JUREQGWRBCFOYV4HI6TG574U/</a>"},{"pid":"f2e92270d6c2907cec3e47305205f9573ad0222d","tid":2422603,"uid":261819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dCzF88A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdCzF88A.gif&h=5220108b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"759ffc5ac164b7f4498f072f678a3cff9275e375","tid":2422603,"uid":258815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:57:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\